17:44.992 --> 18:03.595
his method of operating, but at the same time he 
found him a very delightful person and we really

17:44.992 --> 18:03.595
admired his brilliance and his ability to get 
things done and to inspire people to do things. I

18:04.216 --> 18:22.842
wondered if possibly at that time in 
oceanography, during those years, is that people

18:04.216 --> 18:22.842
such as perhaps Ewing and certainly Revell, 
people who were primarily movers, were needed to

18:04.216 --> 18:22.842
stir up interest or to create interest in this 
newly developing field. Would you agree with

18:22.862 --> 18:27.608
that?

