18:42.540 --> 18:49.591
heroes are sort of product of the situation and the 
environment. A hero would always step forward.

18:54.757 --> 19:05.149
I think we're very fortunate in oceanography in 
having people as, you know, basically as

18:54.757 --> 19:05.149
outstanding as Revelle and Ewing in these roles.

