19:30.275 --> 19:38.586
course, oceanography is much too large to 
identify any people with this amount of influence

19:30.275 --> 19:38.586
or power or control. It's all for the better. I 
mean, we no longer have any heroes unless it's some

19:41.129 --> 19:48.118
sort of very small sub-discipline. This is a 
matter of the size of the field and the way it's

19:49.448 --> 20:07.621
evolved and the fact that we perhaps

19:49.448 --> 20:07.621
look at things a little more sophisticated and 
